title: Real Life 'Ted Lasso'? Apple May Get Into English Football - Just Not AFC Richmond
description: Apple Inc (NASDAQ: AAPL) weighs bidding for the streaming rights to a range of English football games. The rights would allow Apple to show Premier League games in the U.K. and lower league matches run by the English Football League, Bloomberg reports.
